          Format
        </a>
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div id="collapseFourteen" class="panel-collapse collapse">
      <div class="panel-body">
        <ol>
          <li>1. Best of One, Single Elimination</li>
          <li>2. Default server is EU WEST (EU) or US EAST (NA/SA). If both teams agree, the server can be switched. Set mode to CM.</li>
          <li>3. You are to set up your own lobbies for the first 2 rounds, unless a caster or admin call your team to their lobby.</li>
